				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.8-150?lang=eng#7" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:8&ndash;5:3</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote25-20905_000_035">25.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Abraham likened one day in the Lord&rsquo;s time to 1,000 years (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.4?lang=eng#3" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 3:4</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote26-20905_000_035">26.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.1-5?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:1&ndash;5</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.1-5?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:1&ndash;5</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.1-5?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:1&ndash;5</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote27-20905_000_035">27.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.6-8?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:6&ndash;8</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.6-8?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:6&ndash;8</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.6-8?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:6&ndash;8</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote28-20905_000_035">28.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.9-13?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:9&ndash;13</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.9-13?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:9&ndash;13</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.9-13?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:9&ndash;13</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote29-20905_000_035">29.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.14-19?lang=eng#13" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:14&ndash;19</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.14-19?lang=eng#13" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:14&ndash;19</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.14-19?lang=eng#13" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:14&ndash;19</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote30-20905_000_035">30.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See Henry Eyring, &ldquo;World of Evidence, World of Faith,&rdquo; in <span class="emphasis">Of Heaven and Earth: Reconciling Scientific Thought with LDS Theology,</span> ed. and comp. David L. Clark (1998), 59.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote31-20905_000_035">31.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.20-21?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:20&ndash;21</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote32-20905_000_035">32.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.20-23?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:20&ndash;23</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.20-23?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:20&ndash;23</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.22-23?lang=eng#21" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:22&ndash;23</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote33-20905_000_035">33.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.24-31?lang=eng#23" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:24&ndash;31</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.24-31?lang=eng#23" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:24&ndash;31</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.24-31?lang=eng#23" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:24&ndash;31</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote34-20905_000_035">34.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.26-27?lang=eng#25" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:26&ndash;27</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote35-20905_000_035">35.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Note that the Lord called the first man <span class="emphasis">and woman</span> &ldquo;Adam&rdquo; (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/5.2?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 5:2</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 6:9</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote36-20905_000_035">36.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/1.28?lang=eng#27" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 1:28</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.28?lang=eng#27" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 2:28</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.28?lang=eng#27" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 4:28</a>; JST, Gen. 1:30.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote37-20905_000_035">37.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/gen/2.1-3?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gen. 2:1&ndash;3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/3.1-3?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 3:1&ndash;3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/abr/5.1-3?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Abr. 5:1&ndash;3</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote38-20905_000_035">38.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/ps/100.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ps. 100:3</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote39-20905_000_035">39.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/ps/104.24?lang=eng#23" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ps. 104:24</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote40-20905_000_035">40.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.33?lang=eng#32" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 1:33</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.23-24?lang=eng#22" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 76:23&ndash;24</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote41-20905_000_035">41.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.16?lang=eng#15" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 49:16</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote42-20905_000_035">42.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.15?lang=eng#14" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 128:15</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote43-20905_000_035">43.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/2.2-3?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 2:2&ndash;3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.17?lang=eng#16" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 49:17</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.48?lang=eng#47" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 138:48</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.39?lang=eng#38" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">JS&mdash;H 1:39</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote44-20905_000_035">44.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.18?lang=eng#17" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 128:18</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote45-20905_000_035">45.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.32-34?lang=eng#31" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 101:32&ndash;34</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote46-20905_000_035">46.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.30-31?lang=eng#29" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 121:30&ndash;31</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote47-20905_000_035">47.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.10?lang=eng#9" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">A of F 1:10</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote48-20905_000_035">48.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rev/21.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Rev. 21:1</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ether 13:9</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.23-24?lang=eng#22" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 29:23&ndash;24</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote49-20905_000_035">49.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.109?lang=eng#108" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 84:109</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote50-20905_000_035">50.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.110?lang=eng#109" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 84:110</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote51-20905_000_035">51.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.110?lang=eng#109" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 84:110</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.14-26?lang=eng#13" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1 Cor. 12:14&ndash;26</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote52-20905_000_035">52.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/ps/116.15?lang=eng#14" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ps. 116:15</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.8?lang=eng#7" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 42:8</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote53-20905_000_035">53.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/59.20-21?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 59:20&ndash;21</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote54-20905_000_035">54.</a>
      </span>
				<p>The Lord has entrusted us to care for the earth. He said: &ldquo;It is expedient that I, the Lord, should make every man accountable, as a steward over earthly blessings, which I have made and prepared for my creatures. I, the Lord, stretched out the heavens, and built the earth, my very handiwork; and all things therein are mine. And it is my purpose to provide for my saints, for all things are mine&rdquo; (<a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.13-15?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 104:13&ndash;15</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rev/7.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Rev. 7:3</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote55-20905_000_035">55.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/13.34-35?lang=eng#33" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 13:34&ndash;35</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/15.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 15:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/12.10-150?lang=eng#9" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Rom. 12:10&ndash;13:8</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/gal/5.13?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Gal. 5:13</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1 Thes. 4:9</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.11-150?lang=eng#10" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1 Jn. 3:11&ndash;4:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.15?lang=eng#14" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mosiah 4:15</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.123?lang=eng#122" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 88:123</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote56-20905_000_035">56.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See JST, Matt. 6:38 (KJV, <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/6.33?lang=eng#32" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Matt. 6:33</a>, footnote <span class="emphasis">a</span>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-20905_000_035"><a name="-20905_000_035">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote57-20905_000_035">57.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/2.7?lang=eng#6" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Rom. 2:7</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.5?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 75:5</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 128:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.19-24?lang=eng#18" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 132:19&ndash;24</a>.</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
                                        
